# YouTube-Downloader

## Objective: Download any type of video in a fast and convenient way from youtube on your device.
In this python project, 
- user has to copy the youtube video URL that they want to download
- simply paste that URL in the ‘paste link here’ section
- click on the download button, it will start downloading the video
- When video downloading finishes, it shows a message ‘downloaded’ popup on the window below the download button.

### Steps to Develop Python YouTube Downloader
Project Prerequisites: 
(To implement this project we use basic concept of python, tkinter, pytube library.)

    Tkinter is a standard GUI library and it is one of the easiest ways to build a GUI application.
    pytube used for downloading videos from youtube

These are the following steps to build youtube video downloader project in python :

    Import libraries
    Create display window
    Create field to enter link
    Create function to start downloading
    
To sum up: I used the popular Tkinter library that used for rendering graphics and pytube library to download videos from youtube.
